{"data":[{"name":"83:1","price":"1. Woe to Al-Mutaffifûn (those who give less in measure and weight).","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُطَفِّفِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5849,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun lil'muṭaffifīna ","translations":["Woe","to those who give less","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","lil'muṭaffifīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,4755]]}},{"name":"83:2","price":" 2. Those who, when they have to receive by measure from men, demand full measure,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ إِذَا ٱكۡتَالُواْ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ يَسۡتَوۡفُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5850,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna idhā ik'tālū ʿalā al-nāsi yastawfūna ","translations":["Those who","when","they take a measure","from","the people","they take in full","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","idhā","ik'tālū","ʿalā","al-nāsi","yastawfūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1620],[3,1620,2620],[4,2620,3010],[5,3010,4740],[6,4740,7945]]}},{"name":"83:3","price":" 3. And when they have to give by measure or weight to (other) men, give less than due.","arabic":"وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمۡ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمۡ يُخۡسِرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5851,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā kālūhum aw wazanūhum yukh'sirūna ","translations":["But when","they give by measure (to) them","or","they weigh (for) them","they give less","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","kālūhum","aw","wazanūhum","yukh'sirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2210],[3,2210,2500],[4,2500,3750],[5,3750,6895]]}},{"name":"83:4","price":" 4. Do they not think that they will be resurrected (for reckoning),","arabic":"أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin",